CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. A12, reads: "STUNNING...FABULOUS...FASCINATING were just some of the adjectives used in connection with the annual Fashion Show given at Schenley High School by the Beauty Shop Owners and Beauticians.... Center: Jane [Jo Ann] Dickerson and Cora White, a pair of lovely localities, made happy music as they walked across the stage in top flight outfits."
TitMainTitle: Jo Ann Dickerson wearing striped dress and holding round suitcase, and Cora White wearing sleeveless belted dress with gathers at waist, posed in front of ocean background in Schenley High School for annual Beauty Shop Owners fashion show
